K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-0: @364b dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-2: bcom ldan gser mdog ri yi rgyal po 'dra //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-3: 'jig rten gsum mgon 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i sku //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-4: bde gshegs sku yi bkra shis gang yod pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-5: bkra shis des ni deng 'dir bde legs shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-6: bcom ldan dung mdog ri yi rgyal po 'dra //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-7: 'jig rten gsum mgon spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-8: bde gshegs gsung gi bkra shis gang yin pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-9: bkra shis des ni deng 'dir bde legs shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-10: bcom ldan ljang ser ri yi rgyal po 'dra //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-11: 'jig rten gsum mgon phyag na rdo rje ste //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-12: bde gshegs thugs kyi bkra shis gang yin pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-13: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-070:364b-14: dpal rigs gsum gyi bkra shis rdzogs so ////
